{"word":"H7355 - רָחַם - râcham - raw-kham' - Have compassion","slug":"H7355","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָחַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râcham"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-kham'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Have compassion"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D7;&#x05DD; - ra&#x0302;cham</b> - <i>raw-kham'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>fondle</i>; by implication to <i>love</i>, especially to <i>compassionate: - </i>have compassion (on, upon), love, (find, have, obtain, shew) mercy (-iful, on, upon), (have) pity, Ruhamah, X surely."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3395\">H3395</a>, <a href=\"#/H3396\">H3396</a>, <a href=\"#/H3397\">H3397</a>, <a href=\"#/H7348\">H7348</a>, <a href=\"#/H7349\">H7349</a>, <a href=\"#/H7356\">H7356</a>, <a href=\"#/H7357\">H7357</a>, <a href=\"#/H7358\">H7358</a>, <a href=\"#/H7361\">H7361</a>, <a href=\"#/H7362\">H7362</a>"}]}